fields.description:

For moar of Pols work check out his site here https://polcobas.wixsite.com/polcobas 

For moar Moar go here https://www.facebook.com/moarguitars/ or here https://www.instagram.com/moarguitars/

Recorded with Line6 Helix and into a Focusrite Scarlett 2i2 interface.
